snippet.textDisplay: Being a big artist or not, if you make music you know the process of taking your time and making a track that not only the world will want to listen to, but it has to sound perfect to you first. . For people like Frank ocean, Bryson, and Kendrick, I can only imagine that’s what they go through. They are such perfectionist that if It doesn’t sound right to them they imagine it won’t sound right to the world. I make music myself and at least for me that’s what happens to me 70% of the time. Obviously I’m not a big artist but I imagine that is what’s happening with these artist when they take a break.
